# llama-router — LLM Routing Proxy

## What is llama-router?
- VRAM-aware proxy that routes LLM requests to GPU or CPU model variants
- Drop-in Ollama replacement (port 11434)
- Routes to llama.cpp server (port 11435 internal)

## Key Files
- router.py — Main FastAPI proxy server
- sanitizer.py — Request/response sanitization
- config_gen.py — Generates llama.cpp presets.ini from model directory
- group_params.yaml — Model group definitions

## Conventions
- Python, FastAPI
- VRAM monitoring via AMD sysfs paths
- GPU variant: model-stem-gpu (n-gpu-layers: 999)
- CPU variant: model-stem-cpu (n-gpu-layers: 0)
- FORCE_CPU_MODELS env var for always-CPU models
